    "body" : "<p><strong>For older versions of Hibernate (&lt;5.2):</strong></p>\n\n<p>Assuming the class name is Book:</p>\n\n<pre><code>return (Number) session.createCriteria(\"Book\")\n                  .setProjection(Projections.rowCount())\n                  .uniqueResult();\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>It is at least a <code>Number</code>, most likely a <code>Long</code>.</p>\n"
